<strong>Output:</strong> A small Roman style chariot made of brass and plastic, with the words &quot;WATeRCHARIOuT&quot;(sic) written in solid brass across the front. The back of the chariot has been blocked off, creating a hollow compartment to store water inside.</p>
<p><strong>Input:</strong> One bucket of water, one trumpet<br />
<strong>Setting:</strong> Very Fine<br />
