<strong>Output:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">One unchanged pillow</span> One pillow that can change its form, exhibiting properties similar to clay. Output mass and form adjusts to the shape that D-class had moulded it to. Anomalous property observed that output would transform back to its previous shape after approximately 9 minutes if left undisturbed.</p>
