<hr />
<p><strong>Test 914-1649</strong><br />
<strong>Name:</strong> Junior Researcher Boneka<br />
<strong>Date:</strong> 16/07/2020<br />
<strong>Total Items:</strong> One copy of the King James Bible, one copy of the New International Bible, one pencil, one kitchen sponge, one drinking glass, one copy of the Written Torah</p>
<p><strong>Input:</strong> One copy of the King James Bible<br />
<strong>Setting:</strong> Fine<br />
