<p><strong>Addendum:</strong> The output was presented to D-73308, who is blind. He was instructed to interact with the object. When touching them with his hands, D-73308 reported being able to feel raised Braille lettering on the pages, allowing him to read the book in Braille, despite no such lettering being physically present. Item placed in Anomalous Storage.</p>
