<p><em>Note: Aside from that noise, this appears to be an output characteristic of 1:1, which strikes me as being very suspicious. Despite my misgivings, the object passed anomalous screening and seems to have no discernible properties whatsoever. It will continue to be monitored for further developments. - JR Boneka</em></p>
